  3.895238381044298*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[97]:=",ExpressionUUID->"63097166-48d1-4e60-af49-08de3824c211"],

Cell["\<\
The internal impedance of the wires is approximately [eqn 17]:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.746813685999613*^9, 3.7468137073232145`*^9}, {
  3.746813779359541*^9, 3.746813779469839*^9}, {3.7468703024227114`*^9, 
